thank you berty ( sinhala : තෑන ක යු බර ටි ) is a 2010 sinhalese language sri lankan action-comedy film written by tennyson cooray as his directorial debut and starring a number of sri lankan comedians , including bandu samarasinghe , dilhani ekanayake , ananda wickramage , mahendra perera , anusha damayanthi , nilanthi dias , and cletus mendis . the film had its world premiere august 7 , 2010 , in melbourne , australia .